{"tid":1266461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好死]有勇氣輕生，點解冇勇氣反抗？","createTime":"2019-06-29T14:20:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T03:51:17.000Z","uid":137616,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8dd18910f82bfa5a539414df723915bf8b1388","tid":1266461,"uid":137616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:20:16.000Z","msg":"如果已經打算犧牲自己生命，<br />\n代表你已經預左一無所有，已經冇野可以輸，<br />\n既然係咁，點解唔留番有用之軀黎爭取自己想要既野？<br />\n<br />\n見到又多個人犧牲，真係好心痛，<br />\n但係見到咁多人灰左，仲心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你愈無力就中正苦下懷，我知呢一刻香港人好難接受，<br />\n但係我希望想犧牲既人諗清楚，<br />\n既然你冇野可以輸，不如做啲更有用既野<br />\n大家唔好再尋死好冇！求下你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2位烈士rip<br />\n但我相信呢個peace唔係由更多自行了結既生命就換到，<br />\n而係我地200萬+2既不屈去換！<br />\n強權固然難打<br />\n但韓國都抗爭左差唔多半年先可以令總統落台，我地而加先一個月，可唔可以應承我，比啲信心比自己，唔好輕易言敗<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為呢個就係支共既手段，你愈無力代表佢處理愈好</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家，記得珍惜生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e81babadf4578f37f55f6f8bb66b4c6ddd4eeea","tid":1266461,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:21:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b9f6803aaeda4be1a9db007e15d494cdad13482","tid":1266461,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:22:05.000Z","msg":"推多啲正能量post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89ef50e9d3a5aac73f8107d7ef2467c9ac9b12a","tid":1266461,"uid":137616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:22:48.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推，希望大家唔好再咁傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883f6514032d2180671fe925dfb8ddb5b55c0c68","tid":1266461,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:25:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81